// Query: Sign-in result code summary
// Purpose: triage helper, lists every sign-in outcome code and its count
// Data source: SigninLogs_CL (Sentinel Training Lab custom table)
// Reference: 0 = success, 50057 = account disabled,
//            16000 = interrupted (CA/MFA), 50058 = session info missing
SigninLogs_CL
| summarize count() by ResultType
| sort by count_ desc
